<p>Why would Oracle do this in a minor update?</p>

<p>Good question, one reason could be to prepare for multitenancy. In WebLogic multitenancy, they use the name Partitions for the multitenant ‚Äúareas‚Äù, so using Partitions several places meaning different things could be rather confusing.</p>
